Day 18 - Manga 416*
I feel sick, my head hurts and I feel like I am going to puke. It wasn't the book's fault but it could have been. No fucking reason for her to start masturbating, no fucking reason for her to go unconscious and no fucking reason for the collar to be stuck where it was.
1/10.
Not as good as the last one but still good 7/10
